title: Spokane Airport in MSFS gets major upgrade - more detail than ever before!
description:
This week, several airports in the US have been updated, including Spokane International Airport. This airport offers commercial services and is served by nine airlines and three air cargo carriers. Situated in Washington state, the developers have enhanced the airport with numerous details that simulation enthusiasts seeking realism will appreciate.

For a full overview of items added to the marketplace this week have a look at the video below:
